description	"ARC Close Combat - Unique

^2Weapons:
- Strong Melee

^6Equipment:
- Jetpack
- Regenerative Fuel Cells (3)

^8Attributes:
- Melee Resistance
- Heal (3)

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (2) ^3[CS3]

With the rise of more advanced guns, more dedicated fighters are needed in the close combat zone. To combat the advancement, the close-combat fighters have chosen to advance as well.
This one uses a jetpack to reach normally unreachable places, and allows him to get up-close, and quick. Another advancement used is armour plating - they can take more damage than ever before.."